{"id":"b02e436de6bb8c90ee52e599902d7947a965e30c7e84e273d5944f74c8811d68","item_id":"9c33e9bb90:0","text":"Light Filters（灯光滤镜）可在 RenderMan"}
{"id":"caf9f906b16a91cb0160c50abdac8bd6db9a283fa9751f9801ef991554b46a8a","item_id":"9c33e9bb90:1","text":"文档"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"9c33e9bb90:2","text":"中查看完整说明。"}
{"id":"12bfbb8a6b0303dc54d4f9e4a520754757fbd4168e46c9777883b18e51e1ae21","item_id":"9c33e9bb90:3","text":"Adding Light Filter（添加灯光滤镜）"}
{"id":"d6fa5b0de5058c335adbf1b7c9c6981129d2169a14dc718bbd46b0bf1f7d6a7c","item_id":"9c33e9bb90:4","text":"要添加 light filter（灯光滤镜），请在 OBJ pane（OBJ 面板）中通过 TAB menu（TAB 菜单）选择该 light filter。"}
{"id":"223053648015b09f9307d4ef3ecf65fad31fc365af62fb9dd66b2fb04a234cee","item_id":"9c33e9bb90:5","text":"如果希望 filter 从 light 继承 transformation（变换），请将 light filter OBJ parent（设为子级）到 light OBJ 下。"}
{"id":"4f8591a60dbd7e2b5223c19d8f348f4084749500edc5c1ab077acc2aa885b905","item_id":"9c33e9bb90:6","text":"可以对 light filter 进行平移和缩放。最好沿 Z 方向将 light filter 从 light 移开，以避免看到 light filter 的边缘。"}
{"id":"d021b9036081b439ad92bff511b0958bb4f4c874be2fb8dc3942aecbbfa975bd","item_id":"9c33e9bb90:7","text":"Set Light Filter（设置灯光滤镜）"}
{"id":"8c0a9c9d1c3978131a9f7836ed204b97e9ac510696ebc3d9f5e3957b792dbdd1","item_id":"9c33e9bb90:8","text":"将 light filter VOP 拖到 light 的 Light Filter shaders（灯光滤镜着色器）中。"}
